WEBVTT

00:03:59.617 --> 00:04:01.909
and feel its rhymic beat.

00:04:01.909 --> 00:04:04.533
Understanding how this dependable inner pump works

00:04:04.533 --> 00:04:06.871
gives new resonance to the feeling you get

00:04:06.871 --> 00:04:08.061
when you run a race,

00:04:08.061 --> 00:04:09.454
drink too much caffeine

00:04:09.454 --> 00:04:11.831
or catch the eye of the one you love.